Mobil Automation Test With Gauge
================================
Akbank mobil uygulaması için test senaryosu otomasyonu

Scenario : Akbank App Test
--------------------------
* Check that "İyi günler" is seen
* Then click 'En yakın Akbank'
* Check that your location is shown correctly
* Click 'ATM' at the bottom of screen
* Click menu bar on upper right corner
* Click on the third ATM option
* Click 'Yol Tarifi'
* Check Google Maps is opened for directions